<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="favour-vt">favo(u)r <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'feɪvə(r)/    美 /'feɪvər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-to-prefer-sb-sth-to-another">1.★ <strong>较喜欢to prefer sb / sth to another；有利于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Fortune favours the bold / brave. 
天佑勇者。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most students favour the plan,while the teachers are not in favour of it.
大多数学生赞成这个计划，而老师不赞成。</p><footer>人教新选必① – 4</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>favo(u)rable /'feɪvərəbl/ adj   </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>When asked about their opinions about the schoolmaster, many teachers would prefer to see him step aside <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ favor of younger men.  （2011 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. in  </p></div>